<plot>Turning Points is an experimental film set during a college lecture on history. The film examines the fundamental concepts of what history is and then explores the possibilities of alternate history as the professor becomes three separate characters all lecturing on the events surrounding a Cold War crisis in Cuba, circa October 1962.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?621351</url></doc>
